      Creates a new biodiverse place with the given attributes.
      Parameters:
      name - The name of the biodiverse place.
      department - The department where the place is located.
      area - The area of the biodiverse place.
      photo - The URL of the photo of the biodiverse place.

      budget - The budget allocated to the biodiverse place.
